OL,3,CTata Steel's plans for new electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot given go-
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FReporting by ITV Wales journalist
OL,8,FSofia Lewis
OL,10,FPlans to build what is thought to be
OL,11,Fone of the world's largest electric
OL,12,Farc furnaces for steelmaking have been
OL,13,Fgiven the go-ahead in Port Talbot by
OL,14,Fplanners.
OL,16,FSteel giant Tata Steel UK will now be
OL,17,Fable to move forward with its bid to
OL,18,Fbuild an #1.25bn electric arc furnace
OL,19,F(EAF) in the town, which is
OL,20,Fanticipated to be up and running by
OL,21,Fthe end of 2027.
