OL,3,CTata Steel's plans for new electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot given go-
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FThe EAF will be built on the site of
OL,8,Fthe current steelworks in Port Talbot
OL,9,Fin the area of the existing Basic
OL,10,FOxygen Steelmaking (BOS) plant.
OL,12,FWork is set to begin this summer.
OL,14,FRajesh Nair, CEO of Tata Steel UK,
OL,15,Fsaid that "amidst a challenging global
OL,16,Fmarket", the approval was a
OL,17,F"significant milestone".
OL,19,FHe said, "We are very pleased to have
OL,20,Fsecured approval to build sustainable
OL,21,Fsteelmaking in Port Talbot...
