OL,3,CTata Steel's plans for new electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot given go-
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FAround 2,500 people are expected to
OL,8,Fhave left the business by March this
OL,9,Fyear, with many having already left by
OL,10,Fthe end of last year.
OL,12,FA further 300 roles are set to be
OL,13,Faffected in the next three years.
OL,15,FThe company and the Government have
OL,16,Fannounced plans to help find new jobs
OL,17,Ffor those affected, and Tata maintains
OL,18,Fthat the EAF project would preserve
OL,19,Fthousands of jobs in the long run.
