OL,3,CTata Steel's plans for new electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot given go-
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FReasons behind the decision included
OL,8,Foffsetting financial losses, as well
OL,9,Fas a commitment to producing steel in
OL,10,Fa more environmentally-friendly way to
OL,11,Freduce CO2 emissions.
OL,13,FMoving away from producing steel with
OL,14,Fcoal and iron ore ` and instead moving
OL,15,Fto electric-powered steelmaking by
OL,16,Fmelting scrap steel ` will reduce the
OL,17,Fsite's steelmaking carbon emissions by
OL,18,F90%, the company has claimed.
