OL,11,Fconstruction of a new electric arc
OL,12,Ffurnace-based steel production
OL,13,Ffacility."
OL,15,FIt is also planning to construct two
OL,16,Fnew ladle metallurgy furnaces for
OL,17,Fsecondary steelmaking, and supporting
OL,18,Finfrastructure.
