OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FThe company has already signed a
OL,8,Fcontract with Italian manufacturer
OL,9,FTenova to supply the new furnace. Last
OL,10,Fmonth, the company also appointed Sir
OL,11,FRobert McAlpine as the project's mains
OL,12,Fworks contractor.
OL,14,FIn December, Tata Steel said it signed
OL,15,Fa deal with British construction
OL,16,Fequipment manufacturer JCB to supply
OL,17,Fit with 'green' steel from the EAF.
