OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FPrior to the application's approval,
OL,8,FCouncillor Rob G. Jones, representing
OL,9,FMargam and Taibach, urged councillors
OL,10,Fto back the plans.
OL,12,FSpeaking in the Planning Committee
OL,13,Fmeeting on Tuesday, he said that it
OL,14,Fwas "vital" to "retain steelmaking in
OL,15,FPort Talbot."
OL,17,FHe said: "It's come at a cost ` it's
OL,18,Fthe future. Unless we embrace the
OL,19,Ffuture and move forward, we will stand
OL,20,Fstill."
