OL,11,FTata Steel.
OL,13,FShe said, "This is backed by a further
OL,14,F#80m which we are investing directly
OL,15,Finto the community to support
OL,16,Findividual steelworkers and their
OL,17,Ffamilies, businesses in the supply
OL,18,Fchain and on the regeneration of Port
OL,19,FTalbot as we drive future economic
OL,20,Fgrowth in the area.
